WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:01:48.234 --> 00:01:50.404
You know. Levan. you could
say that I did you a favor.

3
00:01:50.486 --> 00:01:51.646
I mean. sooner or later...

4
00:01:51.737 --> 00:01:53.817
Fuck you. Fuck you!

5
00:01:53.906 --> 00:01:56.526
You son of a bitch. You
know what loyalty is. huh?

6
00:01:56.617 --> 00:01:59.617
You know what
loyalty is? Fuck you!

7
00:02:10.256 --> 00:02:13.626
Can't believe you actually
showed up in person.

8
00:02:13.717 --> 00:02:16.297
I can't believe you'd actually
tell me where you were.

9
00:02:17.304 --> 00:02:19.684
Well. you were right about
him being fucking crazy.

10
00:02:23.519 --> 00:02:25.229
So. Matoksa.

11
00:02:27.231 --> 00:02:29.071
A nuclear fallout site
in the middle of Russia.

12
00:02:29.149 --> 00:02:30.569
I assume you have a plan.

13
00:02:32.611 --> 00:02:34.339
- My guy can get...
- I didn't say I wanted to hear it.

14
00:02:34.363 --> 00:02:36.743
Just that you've got one.

15
00:02:37.783 --> 00:02:39.993
I do.

16
00:02:44.123 --> 00:02:47.213
Let me know when you go
in. I'll provide overwatch.

17
00:02:49.211 --> 00:02:50.631
The Agency?

18
00:02:52.798 --> 00:02:54.128
Or just you?

19
00:03:00.764 --> 00:03:02.774
Good luck.

20
00:03:15.237 --> 00:03:18.027
Where the fuck is
Ryan? I need an update.

21
00:03:18.115 --> 00:03:20.218
You stuck your neck out for him.
and if you don't bring him in.

22
00:03:20.242 --> 00:03:23.292
- this is on you.
- I'm still waiting to hear from him.

23
00:03:23.370 --> 00:03:24.890
I'll let you know when
we have something.

24
00:03:40.346 --> 00:03:41.846
Where are we going?

25
00:03:47.144 --> 00:03:49.444
You haven't decided
yet. have you?

26
00:03:56.028 --> 00:03:58.278
There's a quality
you have. Radek.

27
00:03:59.782 --> 00:04:02.792
When you started with me.
I thought it made you weak.

28
00:04:05.537 --> 00:04:07.407
Now I envy it.

29
00:04:09.541 --> 00:04:10.751
What?

30
00:04:12.753 --> 00:04:14.713
Doubt.

31
00:04:19.718 --> 00:04:22.348
You don't have to do this.

32
00:04:37.194 --> 00:04:38.994
Cahill.

33
00:04:39.071 --> 00:04:42.741
It's Greer. Do you have
eyes on Radek right now?

34
00:04:42.825 --> 00:04:44.785
No.

35
00:04:44.868 --> 00:04:47.078
He left the party
with the president.

36
00:04:48.664 --> 00:04:50.464
Shit.

37
00:04:50.541 --> 00:04:53.251
We suspect Radek played a
part in the assassination.

38
00:04:53.335 --> 00:04:56.295
Working under orders from Petr.

39
00:04:56.380 --> 00:04:57.920
You don't think he'd
be stupid enough

40
00:04:58.007 --> 00:04:59.927
to try anything
with her. do you?

41
00:05:00.009 --> 00:05:04.009
If Radek thinks we're on to
him. we can't bet on anything.

42
00:05:05.472 --> 00:05:07.312
I'm on my way.

43
00:05:20.070 --> 00:05:21.490
So...

44
00:05:24.491 --> 00:05:26.911
what will it be. Radek?

45
00:06:48.325 --> 00:06:50.195
- Yes?
- You were with him.

46
00:06:50.285 --> 00:06:52.575
The American.

47
00:06:52.663 --> 00:06:55.373
He was just fishing.

48
00:06:55.457 --> 00:06:56.827
It's nothing to worry about.

49
00:06:56.917 --> 00:06:59.087
Then why are you
inside my apartment?

50
00:07:05.884 --> 00:07:07.684
I taught you well. Radek.

51
00:07:07.761 --> 00:07:09.721
I know what you do
with loose ends.

52
00:07:09.805 --> 00:07:11.805
I've taken care of a
few of them for you.

53
00:07:15.727 --> 00:07:17.937
You sent your wife
and child away.

54
00:07:19.940 --> 00:07:21.900
But there is no
one I cannot find.

55
00:07:22.901 --> 00:07:25.861
Which is why I propose a trade.

56
00:07:25.946 --> 00:07:28.406
My family for yours.

57
00:07:31.410 --> 00:07:33.620
She's fine for now.

58
00:07:33.704 --> 00:07:37.004
We're headed to the
country house. Come alone.

59
00:08:14.870 --> 00:08:16.000
All right. Jack.

60
00:08:16.079 --> 00:08:18.079
Search the facility.
find the uranium

61
00:08:18.165 --> 00:08:19.915
and get out.

62
00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.540
Keep an eye

63
00:08:21.627 --> 00:08:22.747
on your radiation levels.

64
00:08:22.836 --> 00:08:24.626
What do you got?

65
00:08:24.713 --> 00:08:26.673
1.000 millirems.

66
00:08:26.757 --> 00:08:28.677
Is that. you know. uh...

67
00:08:28.759 --> 00:08:30.028
It's fine. Normal
background radiation

68
00:08:30.052 --> 00:08:32.012
is about 350.

69
00:08:32.095 --> 00:08:34.135
Gets dangerous when you
absorb more than 5.000.

70
00:08:46.777 --> 00:08:49.277
The president still hasn't
checked in with her staff?

71
00:08:49.363 --> 00:08:51.373
Not yet.

72
00:08:51.448 --> 00:08:53.698
What about Radek Breza?
Anything from his phone records?

73
00:08:53.784 --> 00:08:56.334
He received a call at
21:40 while at Cáslav.

74
00:08:56.411 --> 00:08:58.961
It was from his wife Jana.

75
00:08:59.039 --> 00:09:01.017
- You check the wife's records?
- Her next call was to book

76
00:09:01.041 --> 00:09:02.631
a flight out of the country.

77
00:09:04.044 --> 00:09:06.554
They landed in
Warsaw an hour ago.

78
00:09:06.630 --> 00:09:08.300
Do we bring IS in?

79
00:09:10.676 --> 00:09:13.596
Radek was head of security.

80
00:09:13.679 --> 00:09:15.679
How do we know who to trust?

81
00:09:22.938 --> 00:09:25.608
The last DDI report's
a bit short on details.

82
00:09:25.691 --> 00:09:27.481
The nuclear accident in Matoksa

83
00:09:27.567 --> 00:09:29.487
was no Chernobyl. but
it doesn't sound pretty.

84
00:09:29.569 --> 00:09:32.359
Hey. I'm a can-do
kind of guy and all.

85
00:09:32.447 --> 00:09:34.317
but this is starting
to feel not great.

86
00:09:34.408 --> 00:09:36.238
Then why hasn't
the meter changed?

87
00:09:38.578 --> 00:09:40.868
I mean. if we were really
heading into radiation.

88
00:09:40.956 --> 00:09:42.642
the meter would definitely...

89
00:09:42.666 --> 00:09:43.876
Do that?

90
00:09:46.628 --> 00:09:47.748
What's the reading?

91
00:09:47.838 --> 00:09:49.378
- 2.100.
- Jesus.

92
00:09:56.138 --> 00:09:58.058
Wait a minute.

93
00:10:00.058 --> 00:10:01.119
Could the reading
really jump that high

94
00:10:01.143 --> 00:10:02.393
in only a couple steps?

95
00:10:02.477 --> 00:10:04.857
I mean. it's rare.
but it's possible.

96
00:10:18.493 --> 00:10:19.873
2.200.

97
00:10:24.166 --> 00:10:26.286
Jack. what are you doing?

98
00:10:26.376 --> 00:10:27.916
What if it's a cover?

99
00:10:28.003 --> 00:10:29.689
You think they
planted radioactive shit

100
00:10:29.713 --> 00:10:31.173
to scare people off?

101
00:10:31.256 --> 00:10:33.336
Actually. it doesn't
have to be radioactive.

102
00:10:33.425 --> 00:10:35.715
Targeted UVC
frequencies could do it.

103
00:10:35.802 --> 00:10:38.432
2.500.

104
00:10:38.513 --> 00:10:40.473
3.000.

105
00:10:40.557 --> 00:10:42.347
This is insane.

106
00:10:42.434 --> 00:10:43.444
3.100.

107
00:10:45.020 --> 00:10:46.440
3.300.

108
00:10:48.607 --> 00:10:49.817
3.500.

109
00:10:52.152 --> 00:10:54.282
Are you really willing
to bet your life on this?

110
00:11:14.007 --> 00:11:15.127
3.800.

111
00:11:21.473 --> 00:11:23.393
1.500.

112
00:11:27.562 --> 00:11:30.192
Yeah. he does that.

113
00:11:39.950 --> 00:11:41.830
We tracked Radek
and the president

114
00:11:41.910 --> 00:11:45.210
to the exit. and this is
where the cameras lose them.

115
00:11:45.288 --> 00:11:48.708
The satellite footage catches
them heading north onto 38.

116
00:11:48.792 --> 00:11:52.052
- Not back to Prague but out into the country.
- Mm-hmm.

117
00:11:52.129 --> 00:11:54.049
Does Radek own any
property out that way?

118
00:11:54.131 --> 00:11:56.591
Only thing registered to him
was the apartment in the city.

119
00:11:56.675 --> 00:11:58.027
Another call
placed from Radek's phone.

120
00:11:58.051 --> 00:11:59.362
- Number?
- Coming up on a list

121
00:11:59.386 --> 00:12:02.596
of unregistered
we've been chasing.

122
00:12:02.681 --> 00:12:04.721
Well. belongs to Petr Kovac.

123
00:12:04.808 --> 00:12:06.098
Run a property check on him.

124
00:12:06.184 --> 00:12:07.944
Looks like a place

125
00:12:08.019 --> 00:12:09.769
- just outside Doksy.
- Send it to my phone.

126
00:12:09.855 --> 00:12:11.040
That's probably
where they're headed.

127
00:12:11.064 --> 00:12:12.404
but I need to be certain.

128
00:12:12.482 --> 00:12:14.152
What does Petr Kovac drive?

129
00:12:14.234 --> 00:12:18.494
The only car in his name is
a 1975 Land Rover series III.

130
00:12:18.572 --> 00:12:20.452
All right. you keep
digging in on Petr.

131
00:12:20.532 --> 00:12:22.742
- I want everything.
- Greer.

132
00:12:22.826 --> 00:12:24.786
We can't keep this from
Czech intelligence.

133
00:12:24.870 --> 00:12:26.960
We've got to at least warn
them of our suspicions.

134
00:12:27.038 --> 00:12:28.708
Fine.

135
00:12:28.790 --> 00:12:32.130
You can read 'em in. but
give me a head start.

136
00:12:52.397 --> 00:12:54.897
Didn't
think you'd answer.

137
00:12:54.983 --> 00:12:56.403
Neither did I.

138
00:12:58.069 --> 00:12:59.949
You know. I was thinking.

139
00:13:00.030 --> 00:13:02.570
most of this makes sense.

140
00:13:02.657 --> 00:13:06.407
Radek resents Russian influence.
so he takes out Dmitry Popov.

141
00:13:06.495 --> 00:13:08.405
Simple assassination.

142
00:13:08.497 --> 00:13:10.997
Inside job from President
Kovac's head of security.

143
00:13:11.082 --> 00:13:14.502
It's kind of standard. really.

144
00:13:14.586 --> 00:13:17.586
But what doesn't make sense.

145
00:13:17.672 --> 00:13:22.012
what never has
made sense. is you.

146
00:13:22.093 --> 00:13:25.143
But I'm starting to get it.

147
00:13:25.222 --> 00:13:27.222
For a while there. I
thought that Radek took her

148
00:13:27.307 --> 00:13:30.887
because we were on to him. but
he took her because of you.

149
00:13:30.977 --> 00:13:35.567
You are the one who
has him running scared.

150
00:13:35.649 --> 00:13:38.439
Americans.

151
00:13:38.527 --> 00:13:41.027
So entitled.

152
00:13:41.112 --> 00:13:43.412
Always thinking you
are five moves ahead

153
00:13:43.490 --> 00:13:45.950
when the game hasn't even begun.

154
00:13:47.452 --> 00:13:50.332
You know. I spent
some time in Russia.

155
00:13:52.582 --> 00:13:56.462
I'd go on walks in Old Arbat.

156
00:13:56.545 --> 00:13:57.915
There was a bakery with a window

157
00:13:58.004 --> 00:13:59.714
that looked right
into the kitchen.

158
00:13:59.798 --> 00:14:01.338
And every morning.

159
00:14:01.424 --> 00:14:05.724
the same guy rolling dough.

160
00:14:05.804 --> 00:14:08.724
Down to the minute.

161
00:14:08.807 --> 00:14:11.887
Then. one morning.
I asked him...

162
00:14:12.894 --> 00:14:14.904
"Why the precision?"

163
00:14:16.481 --> 00:14:18.691
He told me he was Red Army.

164
00:14:18.775 --> 00:14:22.605
And during his years.
every second mattered.

165
00:14:22.696 --> 00:14:25.986
Not for himself.
not for his comrades

166
00:14:26.074 --> 00:14:27.874
but for his country.

167
00:14:31.246 --> 00:14:33.746
It's how he lived.

168
00:14:33.832 --> 00:14:37.842
The past leading the present.

169
00:14:39.671 --> 00:14:41.511
Petr.

170
00:14:41.590 --> 00:14:44.010
It's how you live. too.

171
00:14:47.512 --> 00:14:50.432
He has my daughter. Mr. Greer.

172
00:14:52.434 --> 00:14:54.104
But it's me he really wants.

173
00:14:56.104 --> 00:14:59.864
He will kill her
unless I stop him.

174
00:14:59.941 --> 00:15:02.111
How do I know you
won't kill her?

175
00:17:04.274 --> 00:17:05.404
You seeing this?

176
00:17:05.483 --> 00:17:06.653
I am.

177
00:17:08.069 --> 00:17:11.659
Pull up a high-side search
on Sokol Project. 1969.

178
00:17:27.464 --> 00:17:29.474
This is where
it all started.

179
00:17:31.760 --> 00:17:34.180
Let's hope ours has
a happier ending.

180
00:17:52.530 --> 00:17:54.700
- Everything okay here?
- Yeah. no problem.

181
00:18:31.653 --> 00:18:33.993
Why'd you bring me here?

182
00:18:34.072 --> 00:18:37.162
- Get your hands off of me.
- Alena. you're my president.

183
00:18:37.242 --> 00:18:39.162
My friend.

184
00:18:39.244 --> 00:18:42.004
I'm doing this for
the both of us.

185
00:18:56.052 --> 00:18:57.262
The shed.

186
00:18:59.097 --> 00:19:00.927
Why'd you kill Dmitry Popov?

187
00:19:01.015 --> 00:19:03.515
We're both just means to an end.

188
00:19:03.601 --> 00:19:06.561
I see that now. You will. too.

189
00:19:06.646 --> 00:19:08.146
You don't have to
do this. Please.

190
00:19:08.231 --> 00:19:11.441
If you knew your father.
you'd know I have no choice.

191
00:19:11.526 --> 00:19:13.526
Radek!

192
00:19:15.113 --> 00:19:17.623
Radek!

193
00:19:53.109 --> 00:19:55.029
We need to go.

194
00:19:55.111 --> 00:19:57.071
The Americans are coming.

195
00:19:57.155 --> 00:19:59.195
Let's get all of
this cleared up.

196
00:20:00.533 --> 00:20:02.333
Let's go. come on.

197
00:20:29.479 --> 00:20:31.359
Contact.

198
00:20:31.439 --> 00:20:33.269
We are entering the building.

199
00:20:40.865 --> 00:20:42.865
You seeing that?

200
00:20:42.951 --> 00:20:43.871
Can you boost the signal?

201
00:20:43.952 --> 00:20:45.332
I'm trying.

202
00:20:46.204 --> 00:20:47.294
Jack.

203
00:20:47.372 --> 00:20:50.042
- Split up.
- Let's move.

204
00:20:50.124 --> 00:20:52.714
Jack... Jack. if
you can hear me.

205
00:20:52.794 --> 00:20:54.424
we'll wait for
your confirmation.

206
00:20:54.504 --> 00:20:56.674
Jack.

207
00:24:00.106 --> 00:24:01.606
You all right?

208
00:24:01.691 --> 00:24:03.691
I think so.

209
00:24:03.776 --> 00:24:06.776
- Can you walk?
- I will slow you down.

210
00:24:06.863 --> 00:24:08.873
Come on.

211
00:24:10.700 --> 00:24:12.370
Jack. Rami's down.

212
00:24:15.413 --> 00:24:16.413
Go.

213
00:24:18.416 --> 00:24:20.996
Sending Seiko back to you.

214
00:24:28.384 --> 00:24:31.394
Couldn't have just
shot him. huh?

215
00:24:34.640 --> 00:24:36.310
This is gonna hurt.

216
00:25:18.226 --> 00:25:19.766
Strange...

217
00:25:22.438 --> 00:25:24.438
how the world shifts.

218
00:25:26.025 --> 00:25:28.685
I am old enough to remember
when taking you off the board

219
00:25:28.778 --> 00:25:31.068
would have been a
matter of pride.

220
00:25:35.159 --> 00:25:36.579
What are you doing here?

221
00:25:37.745 --> 00:25:40.785
I can only work from the inside.

222
00:25:40.873 --> 00:25:43.333
Alexei Petrov trusts me.

223
00:25:43.417 --> 00:25:45.997
So you've known about
this plan the whole time?

224
00:25:46.087 --> 00:25:49.467
And thank God for that.

225
00:25:49.548 --> 00:25:53.088
So why don't you tell me
how we're gonna stop it?

226
00:25:55.137 --> 00:25:56.807
We don't.

227
00:26:05.147 --> 00:26:06.187
You okay?

228
00:26:07.984 --> 00:26:09.211
We'll grab you on our
way to exfil. okay?

229
00:26:09.235 --> 00:26:10.235
I'll be here.

230
00:26:10.319 --> 00:26:11.819
Jack.

231
00:26:13.030 --> 00:26:14.530
Jack.

232
00:26:16.367 --> 00:26:18.197
Shit. Let's move.

233
00:26:22.540 --> 00:26:25.000
I can't let you take the device.

234
00:26:25.084 --> 00:26:28.714
Device? So it's a warhead now.

235
00:26:30.631 --> 00:26:33.681
You don't understand.

236
00:26:33.759 --> 00:26:36.259
Sokol is just a tool.

237
00:26:36.345 --> 00:26:40.425
We need to find the
hand that wields it.

238
00:26:40.516 --> 00:26:44.726
Following the device is the
only way I will find him.

239
00:26:44.812 --> 00:26:46.312
Who?

240
00:26:47.356 --> 00:26:49.726
I don't know.

241
00:26:49.817 --> 00:26:52.187
But it all comes from here.

242
00:26:52.278 --> 00:26:55.738
Sokol did not come
back from the dead.

243
00:26:55.823 --> 00:26:57.203
It never died.

244
00:26:59.201 --> 00:27:00.871
You were here.

245
00:27:02.872 --> 00:27:04.712
And I failed to stop it.

246
00:27:06.709 --> 00:27:08.419
I will not fail again.

247
00:27:11.589 --> 00:27:13.419
You must trust me.

248
00:27:22.350 --> 00:27:24.770
Mike. meet me on the south
side of the building.

249
00:27:57.009 --> 00:27:58.139
Eat.

250
00:27:58.219 --> 00:28:00.349
Little bites at first.

251
00:28:02.348 --> 00:28:03.768
I was robbed.

252
00:28:04.850 --> 00:28:07.350
They took me to
the woods. Shot me.

253
00:28:09.313 --> 00:28:12.323
They were vory v
zakone. the bandits.

254
00:28:15.528 --> 00:28:17.778
Vory v zakone.

255
00:28:17.863 --> 00:28:21.033
This country has become
a nation of thieves.

256
00:28:24.870 --> 00:28:27.500
Soon that is all
that will be left.

257
00:28:33.921 --> 00:28:38.801
Each hour alive is but
a keeper of our deaths.

258
00:28:38.884 --> 00:28:40.894
Na zdorovie.

259
00:29:23.512 --> 00:29:25.602
- They made a warhead.
- How do you know?

260
00:29:25.681 --> 00:29:28.311
- Luka's here.
- Fuck's sake.

261
00:29:30.060 --> 00:29:31.730
Come on. move!

262
00:29:31.812 --> 00:29:33.612
You. hurry up!

263
00:29:33.689 --> 00:29:35.769
Let's go!

264
00:33:10.072 --> 00:33:11.492
Got one at 12 o'clock.

265
00:33:11.573 --> 00:33:12.913
Two to the right.

266
00:33:12.991 --> 00:33:15.121
I got one. too.

267
00:33:43.939 --> 00:33:45.609
Jack!

268
00:33:45.691 --> 00:33:48.861
Hotel 60. I need a
hot extract. Over.

269
00:33:50.696 --> 00:33:52.566
Roger. Ten mikes out.

270
00:34:03.584 --> 00:34:05.214
Let's go.

271
00:34:55.677 --> 00:34:57.717
Where's your father?

272
00:34:57.805 --> 00:35:00.265
Why do you want him dead?

273
00:35:00.349 --> 00:35:01.769
You know why.

274
00:35:01.850 --> 00:35:04.480
You just don't
want to believe it.

275
00:35:15.781 --> 00:35:17.741
Did he hurt you?

276
00:35:17.825 --> 00:35:19.275
No.

277
00:35:20.369 --> 00:35:22.409
They will be here soon.

278
00:35:27.668 --> 00:35:29.918
Give me the keys.

279
00:35:31.547 --> 00:35:33.087
- It was you.
- Alena.

280
00:35:33.173 --> 00:35:35.093
There is no time.

281
00:35:35.175 --> 00:35:37.545
The Russian Defence
Minister was you.

282
00:35:37.636 --> 00:35:39.886
Radek. he worked for you.

283
00:35:42.099 --> 00:35:44.139
What have you done?

284
00:35:44.226 --> 00:35:46.226
Everything I could.

285
00:35:51.608 --> 00:35:53.608
Anytime. you guys.

286
00:36:01.910 --> 00:36:04.620
We got you. Come on.

287
00:36:04.705 --> 00:36:05.955
Let's get him ready to move.

288
00:36:06.039 --> 00:36:07.079
Get him down.

289
00:36:18.552 --> 00:36:19.852
We have to go.

290
00:36:19.928 --> 00:36:22.098
No.

291
00:36:22.180 --> 00:36:24.390
Remember the day

292
00:36:24.474 --> 00:36:27.194
when you swore an
oath to your country?

293
00:36:27.269 --> 00:36:31.609
A promise that you would die
for what you believed in.

294
00:36:31.690 --> 00:36:35.490
Many years ago. I
swore the same oath.

295
00:36:35.569 --> 00:36:37.529
I have not betrayed it.

296
00:36:38.822 --> 00:36:41.282
My oath

297
00:36:41.366 --> 00:36:43.696
was to the people
who elected me.

298
00:36:43.785 --> 00:36:47.205
Oh. They didn't elect you.

299
00:36:48.332 --> 00:36:49.412
What are you talking about?

300
00:36:49.458 --> 00:36:51.038
They needed convincing.

301
00:36:51.126 --> 00:36:53.376
A thumb on the scale.

302
00:36:53.462 --> 00:36:55.212
Some help

303
00:36:55.297 --> 00:36:58.547
to show them that you were
the answer to their problems.

304
00:36:58.634 --> 00:36:59.894
No.

305
00:37:00.886 --> 00:37:02.716
I needed access.

306
00:37:02.804 --> 00:37:05.434
And you provided it. LeLe.

307
00:37:05.515 --> 00:37:07.515
Neither of us did
this on our own.

308
00:37:07.601 --> 00:37:09.651
No.

309
00:37:13.899 --> 00:37:16.029
Hotel 60.
we are pinned down.

310
00:37:16.109 --> 00:37:17.503
Copy. danger close.

311
00:37:17.527 --> 00:37:18.897
Changing!

312
00:37:18.987 --> 00:37:20.447
Cover!

313
00:37:26.912 --> 00:37:28.332
Fuck!

314
00:37:34.002 --> 00:37:36.302
Danger close. We are on
station. Have visual.

315
00:37:36.380 --> 00:37:38.720
Tally multiple hostiles
in south hallway.

316
00:37:38.799 --> 00:37:40.319
- Establish prone position.
- Get down!

317
00:37:40.384 --> 00:37:41.514
Three.

318
00:37:41.593 --> 00:37:44.393
Two. One.

319
00:38:00.779 --> 00:38:02.739
This is Hotel 60.
All targets neutralized.

320
00:38:06.076 --> 00:38:07.236
Go!

321
00:38:07.327 --> 00:38:09.367
Let's go! Move!

322
00:38:10.414 --> 00:38:11.874
- Clear!
- Go!

323
00:38:36.982 --> 00:38:38.572
Let's go.

324
00:38:51.538 --> 00:38:53.458
Wright. you there?

325
00:38:53.540 --> 00:38:54.750
We're here.

326
00:38:54.833 --> 00:38:56.593
The weapon's on the
move from Matoksa

327
00:38:56.668 --> 00:38:59.048
- with Luka Gocharov.
- Gocharov?

328
00:38:59.129 --> 00:39:00.459
He's been working

329
00:39:00.547 --> 00:39:03.177
from the inside to find
out who's behind Sokol.

330
00:39:03.258 --> 00:39:04.718
Get out of there. Jack.

331
00:39:04.801 --> 00:39:05.931
Yes. ma'am.

332
00:39:25.113 --> 00:39:26.663
Yeah.

333
00:39:26.740 --> 00:39:28.760
We have a location.
I'm sending you a pin now.

334
00:39:28.784 --> 00:39:30.334
Copy.

335
00:40:47.612 --> 00:40:49.032
Where is he?

336
00:40:52.033 --> 00:40:53.493
Gone.

337
00:40:55.495 --> 00:40:56.865
Alena.

338
00:40:57.873 --> 00:40:59.423
He's not only a part of this.

339
00:40:59.499 --> 00:41:01.919
He orchestrated
the assassination.

340
00:41:04.504 --> 00:41:06.344
He admitted as much.

341
00:41:07.382 --> 00:41:09.552
Popov wasn't the endgame.

342
00:41:12.512 --> 00:41:14.312
We need your help.

343
00:41:14.389 --> 00:41:16.179
You know him better than anyone.

344
00:41:18.226 --> 00:41:19.806
Bullshit.

345
00:41:21.229 --> 00:41:23.229
Nobody knows anyone.

346
00:41:24.816 --> 00:41:26.226
Not really.

347
00:41:48.173 --> 00:41:50.053
See you on the
other side. brother.

348
00:41:50.133 --> 00:41:51.723
Let's move.

349
00:42:09.903 --> 00:42:11.703
We got nothing. Jack.

350
00:42:12.739 --> 00:42:15.079
Let S&T assess all
this. We got to go.

351
00:42:45.438 --> 00:42:46.768
The hell are you doing here?

352
00:42:46.856 --> 00:42:48.146
This is Carl.

353
00:42:48.233 --> 00:42:50.743
That's Devon. They're
going to escort you home.

354
00:42:50.819 --> 00:42:52.399
I live just a
couple blocks down.

355
00:42:52.487 --> 00:42:53.817
I think I can find my way.

356
00:42:54.864 --> 00:42:56.204
Not that home.

357
00:42:57.993 --> 00:42:59.913
You've been recalled.

358
00:43:20.557 --> 00:43:22.137
Mike!

359
00:43:29.566 --> 00:43:31.646
They're building a missile

360
00:43:31.735 --> 00:43:34.775
- to mirror an American nuke.
- Shit.

361
00:43:35.822 --> 00:43:37.822
So when it goes off...

362
00:43:41.119 --> 00:43:43.119
It'll look like we did it.

363
00:43:44.305 --> 00:44:44.818
